They really did.

01:16:51.050 --> 01:16:56.590
I really like this comic because it shows
you what’s going on perfectly.

01:16:56.590 --> 01:16:59.040
Okay, so there are these hippies.

01:16:59.040 --> 01:17:02.560
They’re all friends of this guy named Fat
Freddie.

