They’re basically useless hippies.

01:17:04.430 --> 01:17:09.240
They don’t pay rent and all they do is smoke
pot.

01:17:09.240 --> 01:17:13.820
Anyways, at one point they make a bunch of
money on some cocaine deal and they buy this

01:17:13.820 --> 01:17:16.210
home out in the country.

01:17:16.210 --> 01:17:18.860
They think they’re going to go out there
and live in paradise, so they bring their

01:17:18.860 --> 01:17:23.700
cat along, which is Fat Freddie’s cat who
has his own adventures with cockroaches and

01:17:23.700 --> 01:17:24.920
so on.

